{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"grid semantic tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and expose them."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllGridSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeGridSemanticTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/18OUDSTokensSemantic04GridB6TokensP","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemegridsemantictokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeGridSemanticTokensProvider\/init()"]},{"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeGridSemanticTokensProvider\/GridSemanticTokens-Implementations"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeGridSem